This is your Play application
=============================

To run tests
-------------

sbt clean test

To run
-------

sbt run

Endpoints
=========

GET /getAllClients
--------------------

returns all clients on the database

GET /getAllPets
-----------------

returns all clients on the database

POST /registerNewPet
----------------------

example payload:
{
    firstName: "Sofia",
    lastName: "Cole",
    petName: "Leo",
    petNotes: "Happy and Healthy"
}

adds a client and a pet to the database

